      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">Remove <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">expired</strong> dashboard session rows (Keyv TTL in the past). Does not touch active sessions. Run dry-run first.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <button type="button" onclick="maintCleanupSessions(true)" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold border border-[var(--c-input-border)] bg-[var(--c-input)] hover:bg-[var(--c-card-border)] transition-colors">Dry Run</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="maintCleanupSessions(false)" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold border border-[var(--c-accent-soft-ring)] bg-[var(--c-accent-soft-bg)] text-[var(--c-accent-text)] hover:opacity-90 transition-colors">Delete Expired</button>
      </div>
      <pre id="cleanupSessionsPre" class="hidden text-[10px] text-[var(--c-text-muted)] font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap max-h-28 overflow-y-auto p-3 rounded-lg bg-[var(--c-input)] border border-[var(--c-input-border)] mt-2"></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-5 space-y-3 border border-[var(--c-card-border)]">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">Session Hygiene</h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed">Deletes <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">all</strong> stored dashboard sessions. Every browser must log in again (including yours).</p>
      <button type="button" onclick="maintClearAllSessions()" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold border border-red-500/40 bg-red-500/10 text-red-300 hover:bg-red-500/20 transition-colors">Log Out Everyone</button>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-5 space-y-3 border border-[var(--c-card-border)] lg:col-span-2">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)]">Database Backup</h3>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">Download a JSON snapshot of the Keyv store (same data as the Database Explorer). Keep the file private — it can include sessions and tokens.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <button type="button" id="exportDbJsonBtn" onclick="exportDatabaseJson()" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-[var(--c-input-border)] bg-[var(--c-input)] hover:bg-[var(--c-card-border)] transition-colors text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)] min-h-[44px]">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--c-text-dim)] shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"/></svg>
          Export Database as JSON
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="pt-2 border-t border-[var(--c-card-border)] space-y-2">
        <p class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">Restore from a previously exported <span class="font-mono text-[10px]">nova-keyv-backup</span> file. The server validates the file before any write; use <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Validate</strong> first, then <strong class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">Import</strong> to upsert keys.</p>
        <input type="file" id="importDbJsonInput" accept="application/json,.json" class="sr-only" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1" />
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row flex-wrap gap-2 items-stretch sm:items-center">
          <button type="button" id="importDbJsonPickBtn" onclick="document.getElementById('importDbJsonInput').click()" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-[var(--c-input-border)] bg-[var(--c-input)] hover:bg-[var(--c-card-border)] transition-colors text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)] min-h-[44px]">
            Choose Backup File…
          </button>
          <button type="button" id="validateDbJsonBtn" onclick="validateDatabaseJsonImport()" disabled class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-[var(--c-input-border)] bg-[var(--c-input)] hover:bg-[var(--c-card-border)] transition-colors text-sm font-bold text-[var(--c-text)] min-h-[44px] disabled:opacity-40 disabled:pointer-events-none">
            Validate
          </button>
          <button type="button" id="applyDbJsonBtn" onclick="applyDatabaseJsonImport()" disabled class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-amber-500/40 bg-amber-500/10 hover:bg-amber-500/20 transition-colors text-sm font-bold text-amber-200 min-h-[44px] disabled:opacity-40 disabled:pointer-events-none">
            Import
          </button>
        </div>
        <p id="importDbJsonFileLabel" class="text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-dim)] font-mono hidden"></p>
        <pre id="importDbJsonStatus" class="hidden text-[11px] text-[var(--c-text-muted)] font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap break-words max-h-40 overflow-y-auto p-3 rounded-lg bg-[var(--c-input)] border border-[var(--c-input-border)]"></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


